{"tid":1995322,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［全區最抵黃店］[HKU/西營盤人入] 35蚊一個高質Lunch","createTime":"2020-04-30T07:15:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T17:24:18.000Z","uid":273627,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4b95ea29f4eb07f067663d13ef4fd628394ac7e9","tid":1995322,"uid":273627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T07:15:37.000Z","msg":"話說小弟家境麻麻，平時中西區想食間黃店，閒閒地都要60-80先一個lunch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每次懲罰都真係幾心痛<br />\n<br />\n就算要平少少，最少都要40-50蚊先夠飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都已經唔係話有咩要求，只係求個飽肚就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但今日同個frd試吓呢間係薄扶林道/水街頂嘅黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/65T0Z1O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F65T0Z1O.jpg&h=6c2addd8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sbR2tVc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsbR2tVc.jpg&h=add7c15b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tOHdADj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtOHdADj.png&h=24526254&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AAJwnjL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAAJwnjL.png&h=e19212d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">35蚊一個lunch！ 中/大學生仲要包埋你野飲！</span><br />\n<br />\n除咗賣相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食物質素/味道都好唔錯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RzXw6Jn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRzXw6Jn.png&h=68b30bb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我同個frd食咗成個鐘，除咗我哋，成個鐘都係得<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一個</span>客幫襯咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />已經計埋堂食同外賣都係得一個客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一個鐘得3個客，租都交唔到啊大佬</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n所以唔該大家襯五一黃金週賀一賀佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kK9SRaD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkK9SRaD.png&h=82709e3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你覺得唔方便仲可以叫速遞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果同區有其他黃店推介都唔該下面講聲"},{"pid":"35792d5fa31ba7b018fe92d412fa7b41dd64cb99","tid":1995322,"uid":273627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T07:16:50.000Z","msg":"P牌求幫推黃圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f0b5c9ae8e927d122aa10cbdd964b030a275d07","tid":1995322,"uid":103095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T07:19:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a274c4634773de662612dd12cd14b0b48e26e2a","tid":1995322,"uid":38772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T07:21:00.000Z","msg":"真係好抵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以前最鍾意去"},{"pid":"9d12259d711cdecdbf6a1325baafa1b05a9b1821","tid":1995322,"uid":273627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a274c4634773de662612dd12cd14b0b48e26e2a","tid":1995322,"uid":38772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T07:21:00.000Z","msg":"真係好抵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以前最鍾意去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T07:21:56.000Z","msg":"以前都係呢個價？"},{"pid":"95b25a6f7e51f6af9878e00946b3075646486b62","tid":1995322,"uid":38772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T07:22:59.000Z","msg":"